<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٠⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١١٩٧٨ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ، عَمَّنْ سَمِعَ،<span class="c5"> الْحَسَنَ يَقُولُ:</span> <span class="c2">«إِنْ خَيَّرَهَا فَاخْتَارَتْ زَوْجَهَا فَهِيَ وَاحِدَةٌ وَلَهُ الرَّجْعَةُ عَلَيْهَا»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>